data.title: Episode 2611 (27 October 2003)
data.meta_description: Zoe is forced to make a tough decision. Sonia returns from India. Derek admits that he used to be married with kids. Den Watts - Leslie Grantham Sam Mitchell - Kim Medcalf Kelly Taylor - Brooke Kinsella Zoe Slater - Michelle Ryan Tariq Laroussi - Nabil Elouahabi Ronny Ferreira - Ray Panthaki Kat...
data.text:
Kelly comes home from the hospital and Ronny expresses his concern. She admits taking an E, but will not say who is responsible. Zoe tells Kelly that Ronny cheated on her and Kelly dumps him.

Den tries to find out who sold Kelly the drugs and sacks Sam for not paying enough attention to the drug dealing in the club.

Derek and Pauline have a quiet evening in. He tells Pauline that he has always been gay. He shocks Pauline by confirming her suspicions that he was married and has two children. He has lost all contact with them since his wife caught him with another man.
